<L>__{284. exterior arrakeen palace dusk}
<A>__{paul opens his mouth and issues an ever increasing wind. lightning and thunder begin. clouds begin to form over the palace. in the half light of dusk, thousands of fremen watch the sky. giant golden lights are illuminated and their rays shoot far into the sky illuminating the growing clouds. five tremendous bolts of lightning suddenly unleash a downpour of rain on arrakis. the fremen stand awestruck as they are drenched with water falling from the sky.}
